海洋色彩的雷·米德（Ray Meade）对MS诊断开放：“我以为我已经完成了” https://www.nme.com/news/music/ocean-colour-scenes-meade-meade-opens-up-about-about-mot-ms-diarosis-i-i----------i-i-i-i-was-was-was-done-3849040？ tm_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign =海洋彩色 - 赛车射线射线 - 摩德 - 摩登 -  about-ms-ms-ms-diengnosis-ignosis-i-thought-i-thought-i-i-i-was-donePoppy Burton Tue, 25 Mar 2025 14:56:00 +0000 Music NewsNewsBritpop https://www.nme.com/?p=3849040 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-ray-meade.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="雷·米德（Ray Meade）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-ray-meade.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-ray-meade-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-ray-meade-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-ray-meade-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-ray-meade-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-ray-meade-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我想成为一个例子，即如果您得到它，那不是目的。它是可以管理的。依靠MS护士。您可以继续生活。您仍然可以成为您”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ocean-colour-scenes-ray-meade-opens-up-about-ms-diagnosis-i-thought-i-was-done-3849040">海洋彩色场景的雷·米德（Ray Meade）对MS诊断开放：“我以为我已经完成了”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-ray-meade.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="雷·米德（Ray Meade）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-ray-meade.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-ray-meade-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-ray-meade-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-ray-meade-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-ray-meade-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-ray-meade-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ocean-colour-scene">Ocean Color Spoce</a>的S Ray Meade公开了他的多发性硬化症诊断，称他认为这意味着自己正在“完成”。</p><p>这位吉他手加入了Britpop乐队 - 以其热门的90年代单曲“ The Riverboat Song”和“我们抓到火车的日子”而闻名 -  2016年，本周晚些时候，他们将与他们一起与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kula-shaker">Kula Shaker的</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ocean-colour-scene-announce-2025-uk-tour-with-kula-shaker-buy-tickets-3797790">2025年英国巡回</a>演出。</p><p>在开始进行日期之前，包括在伯明翰，谢菲尔德，伦敦，曼彻斯特，格拉斯哥，利物浦，都柏林等节目之前，米德与<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/cddy84g4102o" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>英国广播公司</em></a>谈到了2021年被诊断出患有多发性硬化症（MS）的演出，以及它如何在精神上影响他。</p><p>贝斯手解释说：“我开始把这些非常强烈的销钉和针头拿到我的手中。这就像滚雪球然后在热水下扔手。这真的很痛苦和热。”</p><p>根据<a href="https://www.nhs.uk/conditions/multiple-sclerosis/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">NHS网站的</a>说法，MS会影响大脑和脊髓，其中包括移动性，疲劳，疼痛和困难的改变，您可以<a href="https://www.mssociety.org.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>找到更多信息并支持。 </p><figure id="attachment_3849058" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3849058" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-3849058 size-full" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-ocean-colour-scene.jpg" alt="海洋色景" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-ocean-colour-scene.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-ocean-colour-scene-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-ocean-colour-scene-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-ocean-colour-scene-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-ocean-colour-scene-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/live-ocean-colour-scene-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3849058" class="wp-caption-text">史蒂夫·克拉多克（Steve Cradock），西蒙·福勒（Simon Fowler）和海洋色彩现场的雷蒙德·米德（Raymond Mead</figcaption></figure><p>米德说，“有诊断几乎是一种解脱，因为它使我能够进行必要的调整并继续我的生活。”</p><p> However, it was coupled with concerns that his career would end. “The day they told me I had MS, I thought I was done,” he said. “I wasn&#39;t even 40 at that point, and I thought I&#39;d have to sell my guitars and find some other way to make a living.”</p><p> After being assured by a neurologist to give it time, he started a new treatment and was ready to leave hospital. Around the same time, Ocean Colour Scene had announced their first tour in almost two years, which gave Meade a focus.</p><p> “My hands didn&#39;t work. I couldn&#39;t tie my laces. I couldn&#39;t do a zip up – I was dropping everything,” he continued, saying he leant on other band members for support. “To have something to aim for was important.”</p><p> At a hometown gig in Birmingham, Meade performed with a stool hidden behind an amp. “In the end I didn&#39;t need it,” he said. “And there was this outpouring of emotion. It was such a terrible time and it was a release to get back to playing live music.”</p><p> Having made his return to live music, he then focused on writing his own, but found his “head was just scrambled with too much information” about MS treatment to write. “The thing to remember is that no one – with my brain – has ever had this before so I needed to find out what&#39;s right for me.”</p><p> He has since released his first new solo work since being diagnosed, &#39;Holy Water&#39;, which came out on <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alan-mcgee">Alan McGee</a> &#39;s new label Creation Youth. You can stream the song <a href="https://raymeade.com/album/3332457/holy-water" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a> .</p><p> “I used to send him demo cassettes. It&#39;s a full circle moment. And to be writing again and to have that music released by Alan McGee meant everything,” he said. “I want to be an example that it&#39;s not the end if you get it. It&#39;s manageable. Lean on the MS nurses. You can carry on with your life. You can still be you.”</p><p> Ocean Colour Scene are set to play the O2 Academy, Leeds this Thursday (March 28). For any remaining tickets, visit <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/ocean-colour-scene-tickets/artist/750020?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=Wio1Vs3-AxyKTIqQnV04UVzBUks3rVQVm2V1Ug0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a> .</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ocean-colour-scenes-ray-meade-opens-up-about-ms-diagnosis-i-thought-i-was-done-3849040">Ocean Colour Scene&#39;s Ray Meade opens up about MS diagnosis: “I thought I was done”</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
